  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink11-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> pāṇaṉ mutalāyiṉārkkut talaimakaṉ koṭumai kūṟi vāyil maṟutta talaimakaḷ
          kaḻaṟiya pāṅkaṟku vāyil nērvāḷ colliyatu ‘talaivaṉ evvāṟu tappiyoḻukiṉum avaṉ koṭumai
          niṉṉāṟ pulappaṭutal takātu’ eṉṟu kaḻaṟiya pāṅkikkut talaimakaḷ colliyatūumām. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink11">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> maṉainaṭu vayalai vēḻañ cuṟṟun</l>
          <l> tuṟaikē ḻūraṉ koṭumai nāṇi</l>
          <l> nalla ṉeṉṟum yāmē</l>
          <l> yalla ṉeṉṉumeṉ ṟaṭameṉ ṟōḷē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> Ashamed by the cruelty of the man from the village that has a ghat</l>
          <l> where wild sugarcane surrounds the purslane planted by the house</l>
          <l> we may [nonetheless] say, 'He is good'.</l>
          <l> 'He is not,' say my broad, soft shoulders.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
